{"tid":1985133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"停工留家太悶 江蘇3男結伴炸屎坑","createTime":"2020-04-23T02:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T03:25:07.000Z","uid":35562,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abadfc397fb89d3ef925ee06ed8faf05a593599c","tid":1985133,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/4/1587466703_VH-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F4%2F1587466703_VH-1280w.jpg&h=5dcb0728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這種行為實在令人無言以對！江蘇蘇州望亭鎮新埂村3名男子因疫情期間停工留家太無聊，於是連日結伴去「炸屎坑」&mdash;&mdash;丟已燃點的炮仗落去屎坑，還拍片留念。飽受炮仗聲及屎臭味困擾的村民報警，警方翻查村內閉路電視後發現，3男去過的地方就有屎坑被炸，至少9戶村民的屎坑受害，其中一個屎坑更被炸多達八九次。警方本月11日拘捕涉案3男，3男承認自上月中至被捕當日炸屎坑廿多次。警方將以尋釁滋事罪移送3男予檢察院起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e5%81%9c%e5%b7%a5%e7%95%99%e5%ae%b6%e5%a4%aa%e6%82%b6-%e6%b1%9f%e8%98%873%e7%94%b7%e7%b5%90%e4%bc%b4%e7%82%b8%e5%b1%8e%e5%9d%91-215946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%2581%259c%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%2595%2599%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e5%25a4%25aa%25e6%2582%25b6-%25e6%25b1%259f%25e8%2598%25873%25e7%2594%25b7%25e7%25b5%2590%25e4%25bc%25b4%25e7%2582%25b8%25e5%25b1%258e%25e5%259d%2591-215946&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6pE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=098dede8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e5%81%9c%e5%b7%a5%e7%95%99%e5%ae%b6%e5%a4%aa%e6%82%b6-%e6%b1%9f%e8%98%873%e7%94%b7%e7%b5%90%e4%bc%b4%e7%82%b8%e5%b1%8e%e5%9d%91-215946</a>"},{"pid":"b2534bf1c8a3892bdfb9997d31e361ad636c8692","tid":1985133,"uid":182061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T03:00:48